import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import useKrakenPrices from "../Cryptos/KrakenApi"; import "./style.css"; const Profile = ({ onLogout }) => { const user = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("user")); const [holdings, setHoldings] = useState([]); const [history, setHistory] = useState([]); const prices = useKrakenPrices(holdings.map(h => h.cryptoSymbol)); const [isSellOpen,setIsSellOpen]=useState("false"); const openSellForm=()=>{setIsSellOpen("true");} const closeSellForm=()=>{setIsSellOpen("false");} useEffect(() => { if (user?.id) { fetch(`http://localhost:8080/api/trade/holdings/${user.id}`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(data => setHoldings(data)) .catch(err => console.error("Error fetching holdings:", err)); fetch(`http://localhost:8080/api/trade/history/${user.id}`) .then(res => res.json()) .then(data => setHistory(data)) .catch(err => console.error("Error fetching history:", err)); } }, []); return (

{user?.name}

{user?.email}

Balance: {user?.balance.toFixed(2)}

Holdings

{holdings.length > 0 ? {holdings.map((h, index) => ( ))}
Symbol Name Quantity
{h.cryptoSymbol} {h.cryptoName} {h.quantity}
:

No holdings yet

}

History

{history.length > 0 ? ( {history.map((h, index) => ( ))}
Symbol Name Type Quantity Time
{h.cryptoSymbol} {h.cryptoName} {h.type} {h.quantity} {h.timePurchase}
) : (

No transactions made yet

)}
{isSellOpen===true?
:<>};
) } export default Profile
